Delicious fondue dinner (to go). I didn't think fondue was something that could travel, but Matterhorn proved me wrong. Fondue was easy to prepare with simple included instructions. Very cute restaurant with lots of decor that will remind you of Swiss! I got Moitie Moitie cheese fondue (served with homemade bread and yummy potatoes), veal, and onion soup.  Both veal and onion soup were great, but the fondue was too alcohol-heavy for me. I also highly recommend s’more fondue!
